<h3 class="endpoint">
    PUT /api/v1/conversations
  </h3>
<p>Perform a change on a set of conversations. Operates asynchronously; use
the <a href="progress.html#method.progress.show" title="progress endpoint">progress endpoint</a> to query the status of
an operation.</p>
